title: Swift shader best settings for smwos
description:
This is strictly for Spider man Web of Shadows.I'm not sure if it's for some other games.But still, the only thing I know is that it runs really fast for Spider man Web
of Shadows.But there is a problem that the game freezes when you start a new game.If this happens to you visit my channel in youtube and you'll find the video.Here's the linkthe demo version so watermark is included.Also, not that only the Swiftshader 3.0 settings make the game run fast.Visit my youtube channel to watch the video or just know it from here that after doing as I say in the settings, set the resolution from the launcher of Spider man Web of Shadows to 800x600. That'll make the game run very very fast.
